<section id="Day1">
<a href="#Day1"><h2>Day1:Delhi - Leh</h2></a>
<p>Board an early morning flight to Leh from Delhi. Upon arrival at Kushok Bakula Airport, in Leh, meet our representative who’ll escort you to one of our listed hotels. Check-in at the hotel. Spend the day resting for high altitude acclimatization. In the evening take a leisurely walk to the local market and visit Shanti Stupa that is beautifully illuminated at night. Overnight stay at the hotel.
</p>
</section>
<section id="Day2">
<a href="#Day2"><h2>Day2:Leh - Khardongla - Leh</h2></a>
<p>The next day after breakfast, proceed to visit Khardongla Pass- the world highest motorable pass. During the drive to Khardongla Pass experience the picturesque view along the winding roads. Later in the day embark on a sightseeing trip covering major hotspots like visit to Magnetic Hill, Sangam of Indus and Zanskar river and Thiksey Monastery which showcases the most photographed statue of Maitreya Buddha in India. Overnight at the hotel.</p>
</section>
<section id="Day3">
<a href="#Day3"><h2>Day3:Leh - Pangong Lake - Leh</h2></a>
<p>In the morning after breakfast, enjoy a full day excursion to Pangong Lake.  The Pangong lake is one of the  most amazing Lakes in the entire Himalayan region. The lake is set to change color 3 to 4 times a day. You may shop at the local market of Leh. Return back to the hotel in the evening. Rejoice overnight stay at the hotel</p>
</section>
